[
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-problem",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "Logcat 最坑的地方，不是报错难。是日志太多。",
    "audio": "logcat-problem/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-problem",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "你一打开 Android Studio，满屏都在刷。系统的，别的进程的，旧的日志，全混在一起。",
    "audio": "logcat-problem/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-problem",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "真正在炸的那一行，常常被埋住。",
    "audio": "logcat-problem/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-problem",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "所以看 Logcat，别硬盯。先把范围缩小。",
    "audio": "logcat-problem/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-problem",
    "step": 5,
    "text": "第一层，只看自己 app。",
    "audio": "logcat-problem/5.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-problem",
    "step": 6,
    "text": "第二层，只看错误。",
    "audio": "logcat-problem/6.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-problem",
    "step": 7,
    "text": "第三层，再按 Tag、关键词、时间继续收窄。",
    "audio": "logcat-problem/7.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-problem",
    "step": 8,
    "text": "再把常用条件存下来。很多问题就不用猜了。",
    "audio": "logcat-problem/8.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "filter-package-error",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "最常用的一条，是 package:mine。",
    "audio": "filter-package-error/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "filter-package-error",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "它只看当前打开项目相关的日志。系统日志和其他进程的杂音，先扔到一边。",
    "audio": "filter-package-error/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "filter-package-error",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "如果要看错误，就加 level:ERROR。",
    "audio": "filter-package-error/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "filter-package-error",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "完整写法是 package:mine level:ERROR。",
    "audio": "filter-package-error/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "filter-package-error",
    "step": 5,
    "text": "接口失败、空指针、崩溃前异常，都适合从这里看。",
    "audio": "filter-package-error/5.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "filter-crash-tag-age",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "程序闪退时，直接查 package:mine is:crash。想看堆栈，就查 package:mine is:stacktrace。",
    "audio": "filter-crash-tag-age/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "filter-crash-tag-age",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "如果代码里有 TAG = LoginActivity，Logcat 里就可以搜 tag:LoginActivity。",
    "audio": "filter-crash-tag-age/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "filter-crash-tag-age",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "只看这个页面的错误，就搜 tag:LoginActivity level:ERROR。Tag 固定以后，定位模块会快很多。",
    "audio": "filter-crash-tag-age/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "filter-crash-tag-age",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "你刚点了按钮，刚进入页面，或者刚复现 bug，就查 package:mine age:5m。旧日志不会再干扰你。",
    "audio": "filter-crash-tag-age/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "saved-templates-core",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "我建议你直接收藏几条模板。日常开发，用 package:mine。",
    "audio": "saved-templates-core/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "saved-templates-core",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "看错误，用 package:mine level:ERROR。",
    "audio": "saved-templates-core/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "saved-templates-core",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "看闪退，用 package:mine is:crash。",
    "audio": "saved-templates-core/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "saved-templates-core",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "这三条先放在最前面。排查时就不用临场拼查询。",
    "audio": "saved-templates-core/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "saved-templates-search",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "查某个页面，用 package:mine tag:MainActivity。查某个关键词，用 package:mine message:timeout。",
    "audio": "saved-templates-search/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "saved-templates-search",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "查最近操作，用 package:mine age:3m。",
    "audio": "saved-templates-search/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "saved-templates-search",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "如果你要查登录页最近五分钟的错误，就用 package:mine tag:LoginActivity level:ERROR age:5m。",
    "audio": "saved-templates-search/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "saved-templates-search",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "这些模板不是背下来就完事。关键是知道每个字段在干什么。",
    "audio": "saved-templates-search/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "fields-core",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "package 是按包名筛。",
    "audio": "fields-core/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "fields-core",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "最常见就是 package:mine。",
    "audio": "fields-core/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "fields-core",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "level 是按日志级别筛。常见级别有 VERBOSE、DEBUG、INFO、WARN、ERROR、ASSERT。",
    "audio": "fields-core/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "fields-core",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "你查 level:ERROR，就是只看错误和更严重的问题。",
    "audio": "fields-core/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "fields-core",
    "step": 5,
    "text": "tag 是按日志 Tag 筛。比如 tag:Network，就只盯网络模块。",
    "audio": "fields-core/5.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "fields-search-time-exception",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "message 是按日志内容里的关键词筛。比如 message:timeout。",
    "audio": "fields-search-time-exception/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "fields-search-time-exception",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "也可以查 failed、null、exception。这些词很适合找接口失败和异常。",
    "audio": "fields-search-time-exception/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "fields-search-time-exception",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "age 是按时间筛。age:30s 是最近三十秒，age:5m 是最近五分钟，age:1h 是最近一小时。",
    "audio": "fields-search-time-exception/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "fields-search-time-exception",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "is:crash 专门看崩溃。",
    "audio": "fields-search-time-exception/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "fields-search-time-exception",
    "step": 5,
    "text": "is:stacktrace 专门看异常堆栈。",
    "audio": "fields-search-time-exception/5.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "query-combine",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "真正好用的是组合查询。",
    "audio": "query-combine/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "query-combine",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "比如 package:mine tag:LoginActivity level:ERROR age:5m。",
    "audio": "query-combine/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "query-combine",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "这条同时限制四件事：当前项目、LoginActivity、Error 级别、最近五分钟。",
    "audio": "query-combine/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "query-combine",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "查业务问题时，这种组合最实用。",
    "audio": "query-combine/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "query-exclude-complex",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "如果某个 Tag 一直刷屏，也可以排除它。",
    "audio": "query-exclude-complex/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "query-exclude-complex",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "比如 package:mine -tag:OpenGLRenderer。",
    "audio": "query-exclude-complex/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "query-exclude-complex",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "它保留当前项目日志，但把 OpenGLRenderer 相关日志去掉。",
    "audio": "query-exclude-complex/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "query-exclude-complex",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "系统日志、渲染日志刷屏时，这招很有用。",
    "audio": "query-exclude-complex/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "query-exclude-complex",
    "step": 5,
    "text": "再复杂一点，你可以同时看多个模块。比如 (tag:LoginActivity | tag:AuthRepo) & level:ERROR & package:mine。它就是看 LoginActivity 或 AuthRepo，同时只看 Error，而且只看当前项目。",
    "audio": "query-exclude-complex/5.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "query-exclude-complex",
    "step": 6,
    "text": "登录、支付、网络请求这种链路，适合这样查。",
    "audio": "query-exclude-complex/6.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-buttons",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "Mac 上看 Logcat，还有几个按钮要会用。",
    "audio": "logcat-buttons/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-buttons",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "Pause 是暂停日志滚动。日志刷太快，看不清时，先按它。",
    "audio": "logcat-buttons/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-buttons",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "你也可以停在当前界面慢慢看。",
    "audio": "logcat-buttons/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-buttons",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "Clear 是清空当前窗口。",
    "audio": "logcat-buttons/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-buttons",
    "step": 5,
    "text": "正确姿势是先 Clear，再复现 bug。这样新出现的日志就很干净。",
    "audio": "logcat-buttons/5.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-buttons",
    "step": 6,
    "text": "Soft Wrap 是长日志自动换行。接口返回很长，或者堆栈一行太长时，打开它会舒服很多。",
    "audio": "logcat-buttons/6.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-buttons",
    "step": 7,
    "text": "New Tab 和 Split 是开新标签或分屏。",
    "audio": "logcat-buttons/7.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "logcat-buttons",
    "step": 8,
    "text": "一个窗口看全部日志，另一个窗口只看错误日志。对比起来会方便很多。",
    "audio": "logcat-buttons/8.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-click",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "你点了按钮没反应。",
    "audio": "scenario-click/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-click",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "先点 Clear。",
    "audio": "scenario-click/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-click",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "再复现一次问题。",
    "audio": "scenario-click/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-click",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "然后输入 package:mine age:2m。",
    "audio": "scenario-click/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-click",
    "step": 5,
    "text": "如果日志还是多。",
    "audio": "scenario-click/5.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-click",
    "step": 6,
    "text": "继续收窄成 package:mine level:ERROR age:2m。",
    "audio": "scenario-click/6.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-click",
    "step": 7,
    "text": "这样就是按最近两分钟和错误级别一起筛。",
    "audio": "scenario-click/7.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-crash",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "如果程序闪退。",
    "audio": "scenario-crash/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-crash",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "先输入 package:mine is:crash。",
    "audio": "scenario-crash/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-crash",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "重点找 FATAL EXCEPTION。",
    "audio": "scenario-crash/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-crash",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "再找 Caused by。",
    "audio": "scenario-crash/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-crash",
    "step": 5,
    "text": "还要找第一个指向你自己代码文件的行号。",
    "audio": "scenario-crash/5.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-crash",
    "step": 6,
    "text": "真正有用的信息，通常不是最上面那一行。",
    "audio": "scenario-crash/6.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-crash",
    "step": 7,
    "text": "Caused by 后面的原因，更值得看。",
    "audio": "scenario-crash/7.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-crash",
    "step": 8,
    "text": "第一个指向你自己代码文件的行号，也更值得看。",
    "audio": "scenario-crash/8.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-network",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "如果是网络请求失败。",
    "audio": "scenario-network/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-network",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "建议你自己统一一个网络 Tag。比如 TAG = \"API\"。",
    "audio": "scenario-network/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-network",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "请求开始打 request start。",
    "audio": "scenario-network/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-network",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "请求失败打 request fail，并把异常传进去。",
    "audio": "scenario-network/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-network",
    "step": 5,
    "text": "然后 Logcat 里直接查 tag:API。",
    "audio": "scenario-network/5.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-network",
    "step": 6,
    "text": "只看错误，就查 tag:API level:ERROR。",
    "audio": "scenario-network/6.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-network",
    "step": 7,
    "text": "这样请求开始、成功、失败、异常。",
    "audio": "scenario-network/7.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "scenario-network",
    "step": 8,
    "text": "会在一条线上。",
    "audio": "scenario-network/8.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-good-tags",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "日志写得好，后面排查会轻松很多。",
    "audio": "write-good-tags/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-good-tags",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "Tag 要固定，也要有意义。别写 aaa、bbb 这种 Tag。",
    "audio": "write-good-tags/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-good-tags",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "你过两天回来，自己都不知道它是谁。",
    "audio": "write-good-tags/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-good-tags",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "推荐写 LoginActivity、Network、Order 这种。",
    "audio": "write-good-tags/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-good-tags",
    "step": 5,
    "text": "比如 private const val TAG = \"LoginActivity\"。",
    "audio": "write-good-tags/5.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-good-tags",
    "step": 6,
    "text": "后面就能直接按 Tag 搜。",
    "audio": "write-good-tags/6.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-good-tags",
    "step": 7,
    "text": "团队里别人也看得懂。",
    "audio": "write-good-tags/7.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-errors-context",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "错误日志优先用 Log.e。",
    "audio": "write-errors-context/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-errors-context",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "比如 Log.e(\"Network\", \"request failed\", e)。",
    "audio": "write-errors-context/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-errors-context",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "这样你用 level:ERROR 一筛，问题日志就出来了。",
    "audio": "write-errors-context/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-errors-context",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "普通调试日志和真正错误，也更容易分开。",
    "audio": "write-errors-context/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-errors-context",
    "step": 5,
    "text": "还要记得打关键上下文。比如提交订单时，不要只写 submit。",
    "audio": "write-errors-context/5.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-errors-context",
    "step": 6,
    "text": "写成 submit order, userId=$userId, productId=$productId。",
    "audio": "write-errors-context/6.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-errors-context",
    "step": 7,
    "text": "这样你回头一看，就知道是哪个用户。",
    "audio": "write-errors-context/7.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "write-errors-context",
    "step": 8,
    "text": "也知道提交了哪个商品。当时传了哪些参数，也能看见。",
    "audio": "write-errors-context/8.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "three-commands",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "如果你现在只想记三条。",
    "audio": "three-commands/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "three-commands",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "那就记 package:mine。",
    "audio": "three-commands/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "three-commands",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "再记 package:mine level:ERROR。",
    "audio": "three-commands/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "three-commands",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "再记 package:mine is:crash。",
    "audio": "three-commands/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "three-commands",
    "step": 5,
    "text": "第一条看自己项目。",
    "audio": "three-commands/5.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "three-commands",
    "step": 6,
    "text": "第二条看自己项目的错误。",
    "audio": "three-commands/6.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "three-commands",
    "step": 7,
    "text": "第三条看自己项目的崩溃。这三条已经能解决很多新手调试问题。",
    "audio": "three-commands/7.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "cheat-sheet-close",
    "step": 1,
    "text": "这里留一个速查版。",
    "audio": "cheat-sheet-close/1.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "cheat-sheet-close",
    "step": 2,
    "text": "看当前项目：package:mine。看当前项目错误：package:mine level:ERROR。看当前项目崩溃：package:mine is:crash。",
    "audio": "cheat-sheet-close/2.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "cheat-sheet-close",
    "step": 3,
    "text": "看某个页面：package:mine tag:MainActivity。看某个关键词：package:mine message:timeout。看最近五分钟：package:mine age:5m。",
    "audio": "cheat-sheet-close/3.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "cheat-sheet-close",
    "step": 4,
    "text": "看某模块最近五分钟错误：package:mine tag:LoginActivity level:ERROR age:5m。",
    "audio": "cheat-sheet-close/4.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "cheat-sheet-close",
    "step": 5,
    "text": "排除刷屏 Tag：package:mine -tag:OpenGLRenderer。",
    "audio": "cheat-sheet-close/5.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "cheat-sheet-close",
    "step": 6,
    "text": "Logcat 不怕日志多。",
    "audio": "cheat-sheet-close/6.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "cheat-sheet-close",
    "step": 7,
    "text": "怕的是你没有筛选方法。",
    "audio": "cheat-sheet-close/7.mp3"
  },
  {
    "chapter": "cheat-sheet-close",
    "step": 8,
    "text": "以后别硬看整屏日志。先缩小范围，再找错误点。",
    "audio": "cheat-sheet-close/8.mp3"
  }
]
